## Tự Động Review Checklist

### ⛔ HARD RULES (FAIL nếu vi phạm)

> Variables: `{{SCREEN_BASE_CLASS}}`, `{{SCREEN_STATE_BASE}}`, `{{CONSUMER_BASE}}`, `{{PROVIDER_BASE}}`, `{{BRAND}}`, `{{TEXT_DEFAULT}}`, `{{I18N_CLASS}}`, `{{STATE_TYPE}}`, `{{M_SHOW_DIALOG}}`, `{{M_SHOW_TOAST}}`, `{{SVG_HELPER}}`, `{{TEXT_STYLE_CLASS}}`, `{{BTN_CLASS}}`.

- [ ] **Screen dùng `{{SCREEN_STATE_BASE}}`** — KHÔNG dùng `Scaffold` trực tiếp
  ```dart
  // ❌ FAIL
  return Scaffold(
    backgroundColor: ColorApp.backgroundDefault,
    appBar: AppBar(title: Text({{I18N_CLASS}}.title)),
    body: ProgressHUD(
      child: {{CONSUMER_BASE}}<XxxService, XxxProvider>(...),
    ),
  );

  // ✅ PASS
  class XxxScreen extends {{SCREEN_BASE_CLASS}} { ... }
  class _XxxScreenState extends {{SCREEN_STATE_BASE}}<XxxScreen, XxxService, XxxProvider> {
    @override
    Widget buildBody(BuildContext context) {
      return {{CONSUMER_BASE}}<XxxService, XxxProvider>(...);
    }
  }
  ```

- [ ] **Body Widget KHÔNG chứa `Scaffold` / `AppBar` / `ProgressHUD`**
  ```dart
  // ❌ FAIL — Body bị bọc lại
  class BodyXxxWidget extends StatefulWidget {
    @override
    Widget build(BuildContext context) {
      return Scaffold(                        // ❌
        appBar: AppBar(...),                // ❌
        body: ProgressHUD(                  // ❌
          child: {{CONSUMER_BASE}}<XxxService, XxxProvider>(...),
        ),
      );
    }
  }

  // ✅ PASS — Body chỉ chứa content
  class BodyXxxWidget extends StatelessWidget {
    @override
    Widget build(BuildContext context) {
      return {{CONSUMER_BASE}}<XxxService, XxxProvider>(
        onRepositorySuccess: (repo) => ...,
      );
    }
  }
  ```

- [ ] **Auto-detect vi phạm bằng grep**
  ```bash
  if grep -q "return Scaffold(" *_screen.dart; then
    echo "❌ FAIL: Screen dùng Scaffold trực tiếp"
  fi

  if grep -q "appBar: AppBar\|return ProgressHUD(" widget/body_*.dart; then
    echo "❌ FAIL: Body widget có AppBar/ProgressHUD"
  fi
  ```

